            aspernatur eum, reprehenderit molestias distinctio alias maiores
            enim labore obcaecati. Amet quaerat excepturi, illo iure esse
            perferendis earum nam porro architecto cupiditate voluptates
            consectetur sapiente? Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur
            adipisicing elit. Distinctio fugiat quam similique.
          </p>

          <a
            href="/about"
            class="font-bold prose mb-2 flex text-purple-500 underline-offset-4 underline"
